Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Story That Concludes in the Light"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, this is my final trump card as well as my mightiest warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atem still had the Black Magician in his deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was reassuring when he was on my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But as an enemy, there's no stronger foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have to defeat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or I won't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon a Monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician's Attack Power with the equipped Book of Secret Arts is 2800.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}None of my current Monsters can beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Curse of Dragon into Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's got nothing else he can do but defend...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we don't know that for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Face-Down Defense Monster could be troublesome for Atem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monster set on Partner's field...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And by using Witch of the Black Forest's Effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can add a Monster with 1500 Defense Points or less
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in this case Marshmallon, from my deck into my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's without a doubt Marshmallon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When that thing is attacked while in Face-Down Defense Position,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it deals 1000 points of damage to the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's a Monster that can't be destroyed in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Life is at 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I attack him carelessly, this match will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, my partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such a strategy won't work against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Thousand Knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh's really forming his own cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no doubt that the Pharaoh is now God of Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Thousand Knives is on the field with a Black Magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can destroy one of the opponent's Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marshmallon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the effect of Marshmallon in Face-Down Defense Position won't activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Curse of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, Yugi had the advantage, but he just lost all his Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:04:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He changed the flow of this battle in an instant...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Magician is really frightening...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My other self and the Black Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there even a blind spot in the formidable bond these two share...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn now, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Blockman from my hand in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then set a card face-down... and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip Black Magician with the Black Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Black Magician is equipped with the Black Sphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and its Attack Power is higher than the opponent's Defense Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the difference is dealt to the player as damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician, attack Blockman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Shield lets me halve my Life and negate the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent's Battle Phase is then forced to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Magician's attack couldn't reach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then my turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made it out of that one somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now Yugi's only got 400 Life Points remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Atem-{\i1}kun{\i0} only has 700 of his Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be all that farfetched to think the next attack will determine the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit. I was talking all high and mighty to get Anzu to stay and watch this Duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but now I'm starting to feel like I can't watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... Atem...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fate is too cruel to force you two to fight each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's planning something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no choice but to make a gamble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play a Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Gold Sarcophagus of Sealing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gold Sarcophagus of Sealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can choose a card and place it inside the gold sarcophagus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my opponent uses the same card, its effect is negated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What card did he choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That box...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks exactly the same as the box Yugi kept his Millennium Puzzle in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The box the Millennium Puzzle was laid to rest in...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The object that lead to Yugi and the other Yugi meeting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A box of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then activate Blockman's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Block Release!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blockman has the ability to split into the same number of sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the number of turns passed since his Summoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Blockman becomes two offerings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice the two Blockmans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll defeat the Black Magician with this Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandora, the Dragon of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandora, the Dragon of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gandora...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monster that defeated Bakura's dark personality in the Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's the Monster that represents Yugi's parting with the other Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the turn Gandora, the Dragon of Destruction appears on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its effect halves the Life of the player
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and removes all the Monsters on the field from the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandora's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giga Rays of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card, Black Illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon activation, it protects Black Magician from all Monster Effects on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Gandora couldn't defeat the Black Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as a result of this effect, the opponent is permitted to draw another card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi just lost all his Monsters on the field again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for Yugi this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really isn't possible for Vessel Yugi to defeat the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... Partner's flame of opposition hasn't disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Black Magician will attack you directly, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician's Circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my opponent attacks with a Magician Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this card lets me Special Summon a Spellcaster-Type Monster from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a card meant to deal with Black Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Partner really did think up a strategy to battle against Black Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Silent Magician from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Magician's Circle calls out to {\i1}my deck{\i0} as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will continue, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Silent Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's Monster only has 1000 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this hits him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't over, Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swore to defeat you in this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Textbook of Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this card to discard my entire hand and draw one card from my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's a Magic Card, I can activate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand is at zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}have{\i0} no cards to discard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This will be the last draw that determines both of our fates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure From Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both players draw cards from their decks until they hold six cards in their hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this moment to activate Silent Magician's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent Magician's Attack Power increases by 500 points every time my opponent draws a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to draw five cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, Silent Magician advances to Level Five and her Attack Power becomes 3500!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Black Magician's attack will continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atem's only got 700 of his Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this Battle Phase is conducted, Yugi will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Quick-Play Magic from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magicians Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there are more than two Spellcaster-Type Monsters on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use two of my Magicians to launch a 3000 Attack Point attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to defeat my trump card, the Black Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our Life Points are tied at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't continue much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to settle this has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, the card you used to turn the tables, Treasure From Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in turn gave {\i1}me{\i0} a turnaround.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guided me to just the card I {\i1}needed{\i0} to settle this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Resurrection of the Dead, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrect, God of the Sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought Osiris back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris' Attack Power is determined by the amount of cards the player has in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have five cards in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that Osiris\N has 5000 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner... I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew, Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were you... I would call out a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now break the seal on the gold sarcophagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sealed card is coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I put Resurrection of the Dead in the coffin, you can't use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, on this turn... Osiris' Special Summoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is negated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...fading away...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead is usually the card that gives Yugi the upper hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet he sealed it away himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Yugi's message... to the other Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The souls of the {\i0}dead{\i1} must not linger in the world of the living...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was meant as a requiem to see that the Pharaoh's soul travels to the Afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi's trump card... was also his way of saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Partner... predicted my trump card...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've... {\i0}surpassed{\i1} me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atem-{\i1}kun{\i0} doesn't have any Wall Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Silent Magician attacks him directly... the Duel is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now come...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack on the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lose, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}winner{\i0} shouldn't be on his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I wouldn't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm too {\i1}weak{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been my {\i1}goal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to be {\i1}strong{\i0}... like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}not{\i0} weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've {\i1}always{\i0} had a power that no one else could beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strength of {\i1}kindness{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I learned from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}courage{\i0} you showed when you accepted this Battle Ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...showed me the path I must take.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the "other you" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are no one but {\i1}yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the {\i1}only Yugi Mutou{\i0} in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eye on the door...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of Wadjet guards the door to the Afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through the Rite of the Duel, it has seen through the Pharaoh's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After 3,000 years of being {\i1}lost{\i0} in the world of the living,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the time has come for the Pharaoh's soul to be {\i1}welcomed{\i0} into the {\i1}next world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul of the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say your name to the Eye of Wadjet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Atem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yugi!!\N - Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't really have to go the next world, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't leave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... Atem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place you have to return lies beyond that light...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}know{\i0} that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to {\i1}us,{\i0} that light is nothing but a {\i1}wall{\i0} separating you from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you... understand what that {\i1}means{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been friends for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now all of a sudden you're just going to vanish right in front of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't {\i1}get it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu! You don't {\i1}need{\i0} to get it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just {\i1}accept it{\i0} and burn these memories into your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time you've spent with him... The feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it in so you {\i1}never forget!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So for {\i1}now{\i0}... Let's just see him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To his {\i1}future!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...anything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're "Pharaoh", even if you're "Atem",
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're still "Yugi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a thousand years pass, we'll always be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stone Slab of the Underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Items!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By delivering the Pharaoh's soul, the role of the Millennium Items has {\i1}ended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Door to the Afterlife has closed forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's gone, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:22:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mornin'!\N - Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're late, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8} Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't the story of a great Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Everyone{\i1} has a story of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that story ends in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My story has just begun!
